<author>ṣfwt fwzy, nạdr jwrj</author>
<title>rwḥy yạ mḥbwsẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rwḥy yạ mḥbwsẗ mạ byn ḥyṭạn ạlyạ̉s
 kẖạyf ʿly̱ bkrh yḍyʿ bdẖnb ạlạ̉ms
 ḥly ạlqywd ḥly mn ḥmlk ạtḥly
 ạrmy ʿlyh hmy m ạlʿtmẗ tṭlʿ sẖms
 2- yạ sẖms bkrh myly ʿly̱ myly
 nạsy dmwʿ ạlạ̉ms rạfʿ trạtyly
 bạṣrkẖ fy wsẖ ạlfsẖl kạtb ʿly̱ hdwmy
 ḥạḍn ạ̉nạ bkrh zydy fy qlby zydy
 3- ṣwtk byhms ly ynsẖlny mn yạ̉sy
 ạrkb ḥṣạn ạlạ̉ml wạ̉msk ljạm nfsy
 ttsẖd ạ̉wtạry ạ̉bny hmwm ywmy ytfk ạ̉sr ạlrwḥ
 tmḥy dẖnwb ạ̉msy</lyrics>
</song>